15 4 to honor the sacrifices and dedication of firefighters across the
16 nation, who risk their lives to protect communities and save lives
17 from the devastation of fire and other emergencies; and
18 WHEREAS, firefighters demonstrate unwavering courage,
19 selflessness, and resilience in the face of danger, exemplifying the
20 highest ideals of service to others and commitment to public safety;
21 and
