12 important and courageous work of the firefighters of Oklahoma; and
13 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
14 OF THE 1ST SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
15 THAT the Oklahoma House of Representatives declares May 4, 2025,
